    "Deep learning models, including the pre-trained Keras Neural Network and RestNet CNN, demonstrate the potential for accurate hand presence classification when integrated with contact sensor technology [40].Table 1 offers an organized summary of key research studies focusing on hand classification, presenting an overview of significant contributions in this area.A powerful approach to enhance on-wheel hand action recognition and prioritize driver safety is utilizing feature trajectories, which is the technique to track the path or progression of specific features or characteristics over time."
